puls-g3 (0.8.0) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Displays Memory Type, Generation, Speed (MT/s), and Temperature, may require sudo
  * Added Read and Write rate columns for individual disks and improved NVMe detection
  * Restored Memory Clock and added PCIe version/width display
  * Added version display to top-left of the header bar
  * Made navigation bar scrollable and status labels wrapping for better resizing
  * Fixed NVMe temperature detection to match original PULS reliability
  * Normalized load average by core count for accurate ratings
  * Fixed border color mismatch and data display issues
  * Updated grid to 8 columns for better visibility
  * Reduced navigation button size for a more compact look

